## dbt Fusion Engine (Evaluation Phase)

dbt Labs released the **Fusion engine** (Rust-based, 30x faster parsing) with a free VS Code extension.
Fusion works with dbt Core locally (no dbt Cloud required).

**What Fusion adds:**
- IntelliSense: autocomplete for `ref()`, `source()`, column names
- Live error detection: catches compilation errors as you type
- Instant parse times (milliseconds instead of seconds for large projects)
- Column-level lineage visualization in VS Code

**Status:** Under evaluation (see T-23.4 in UNIFIED_BACKLOG.md).
**Do not** require Fusion for any current development work.
If you have Fusion installed, the `dbt` MCP server will auto-detect it.

